<a href="4jb76.html">Jacket Copy</a><br>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>
<p>
</p><p>
</p><p>Vincenzo Ruggiero is Reader in Criminology and Social Studies at Middlesex University; Mick Ryan is Professor of Penal Politics at the University of Greenwich; and Joe Sim in Professor of Criminology at the Liverpool John Moores University. <br>
</p>
