</p><br>
<a href="7jb204.html">Jacket Copy</a>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>
Mary Kay Zuravleff was born in 1960 and grew up in Oklahoma City. She
works as an editor of books and exhibition texts at the Smithsonian Institution
in Washington DC, where she lives with her husband and son. This is her first
novel.
