<h2>V<font size=-1>IETNAMERICA</font>.<br></h2>
<p> By Thomas Bass. <br>
<i>Soho Press; 278 pages; $25</i><br>
</p><br>
<a href="9jb261.html">Jacket Copy</a>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>
Thomas A. Bass authored The Eudaemonic Pie, Reinventing the Future:
Conversations with the World 's Leading Scientists and Camping with the
Prince and Other Tales of Science in Africa. He has written for Wired,
Smithsonian, Audubon, Pacific News Service, Omni, Discover and The New
York Times.
