<h2>M<font size=-1>YTH</font> <font size=-1>AND</font> M<font size=-1>EASUREMENT</font>:<br> T<font size=-1>HE</font> N<font size=-1>EW</font> E<font size=-1>CONOMICS</font> <font size=-1>OF THE</font> M<font size=-1>INIMUM</font> W<font size=-1>AGE</font><br></h2>
<p>By David Card and Alan Krueger.<br>
<i> $29.95 and</i> <i>&#163;25.</i><br>
</p><br>
<a href="3jb47.html">Jacket Copy</a><br>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>
<p>
</p><p>
</p><p>David G. Blanchflower is Professor of Economics at Dartmouth College, and Research Associate at the National Bureau of Economic Research. Andrew J. Oswald is Senior Research Fellow at the London School of Economics. He works in the Centre for Economic Performance, which is funded by the British Economic and Social Research Council. <br>
