<h2>A<font size=-1>CCOUNTING</font> <font size=-1>FOR</font> G<font size=-1>ROWTH</font>.<br></h2>
<p> By Terry Smith. <br>
<i>Century Ltd; 216 pages; &#163;14.99</i> <br>
</p><br>
<a href="9jb269.html">Jacket Copy</a>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>
Terry Smith is a stockbroker who specialises in the analysis of company
accounts. For many years he was voted the leading bank analyst in surveys of
institutional investors.
<p><a href="http://www.economist.com/index.html"><i>The Economist</i> Home Page</a>
