<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 border=0>
<tr><td valign=bottom align=left><img src="http://www.economist.com/review/images/instrap.gif"></td><td>
<h2>M<font size=-1>EN IN </font>B<font size=-1>LACK</font><br></h2>
<p>By John Harvey.<br>
<i>Reaktion Books; 280 pages; &#163;19.95</i><br>
</p><br>
<a href="3jb23.html">Jacket Copy</a><br>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>
<p>
</p><p>
</p><p>John Harvey is a Lecturer in English at the University of Cambridge. His books include Vistorian Novelists and their Illustrators. <br>
</p>
<p><a href="http://www.economist.com/index.html"><i>The Economist</i> Home Page</a> &nbsp; - &nbsp; <a href="http://www.economist.com/cgi-bin/search_form.cgi?824508000,rev">Search</a>
