http://www.economist.com:80/review/rev8/rv4/review.html 199.173.162.110 19970113182246 text/html 5865
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 18:18:54 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 25-Jul-96 18:55:22 GMT
Content-length: 5680
