<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/review/rev4/rv18/review.html 199.173.162.110 19970113185312 text/html 7363
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 18:49:24 GMT
