<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/review/rev7/rv2/review.html 199.173.162.110 19970113182818 text/html 7283
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 18:24:30 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 08-Aug-96 14:04:12 GMT
