<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/review/rev8/rv12/review.html 199.173.162.110 19970113182535 text/html 5467
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 18:21:48 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 25-Jul-96 18:55:21 GMT
Content-length: 5282
