<h2>P<font size=-1>UPPET</font> M<font size=-1>OTEL</font>.<br></h2>
<p> By Laurie Anderson. <br>
<i>Voyager</i><br>
</p><br>
<a href="9jb251.html">Jacket Copy</a>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>
About the Author: Diva of the avant-garde, Laurie Anderson is America's
premiere performance artist. Over the past twenty years, she has worled as an
artist, composer, author, political commentator, photographer, filmmaker, and
musician. Anderson's sixth album, Bright Red (Warner), was released in
October 1994, and her seventh, The Ugly One with the Jewels and Other
Stories (Warner), in March 1995.
