<DOCOLDNO>IA069-000432-B017-281</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/review/rev12/rv1/review.html 199.173.162.110 19970113123605 text/html 8205
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 12:32:22 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 03-Dec-96 18:24:34 GMT
