http://www.economist.com:80/review/rev11/rv5/review.html 199.173.162.110 19970113180029 text/html 5852
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 13-Jan-97 17:56:43 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 14-Nov-96 16:28:47 GMT
