<DOCNO>WT22-B01-404</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA026-000279-B022-366</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.economist.com:80/review/rev4/rv13/review.html 199.173.162.110 19970113185052 text/html 7412
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
