<h2>T<font size=-1>HE</font> C<font size=-1>OMING</font> R<font size=-1>USSIAN</font> B<font size=-1>OOM</font>.<br></h2>
<p> By Richard Layard and John Parker. <br>
<i>Free Press; 380 pages; $27.50</i>. <i>Simon and Schuster; &#163;18.99</i><br>
</p><br>
<a href="11jb334.html">Jacket Copy</a>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>
RICHARD LAYARD is a Professor at the London School of Economics and Political Science and an
advisor to Boris Yeltsin.
<p>JOHN PARKER is formerly a Moscow correspondent and currently the European Editor of The Economist. He, like Professor Layard, lives in London. </p>
<p><a href="http://www.economist.com/index.html"><i>The Economist</i> Home Page</a>
