<h2>C<font size=-1>RISIS</font> <font size=-1>IN</font> <font size=-1>THE</font> A<font size=-1>CADEMY</font>.<br></h2>
<p> By Christopher Lucas. <br>
<i>St. Martin's Press; 288 pages;</i> <i>$29.95.</i><br>
</p><br>
<a href="10jb295.html">Jacket Copy</a>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>
CHRISTOPHER J. LUCAS is Professor of Higher Education and Head of the
Department of Educational Leadership, Counseling, and Foundations at the
University of Arkansas at Fayetteville. He is the author of American Higher
Education: A History and ten other books.
