<a href="11jb339.html">Jacket Copy</a>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>
About the author
John Roberts was, until his retirement in 1994, Warden of Merton College,
Oxford. Author of History of the World and Shorter Illustrated History of the
World (both published by Helicon), he has also published several academic
works and is General Editor of the Short Oxford History of the Modern World
and The New Oxford History of Engsand. He also wrote and presented the
BBC television series The Triumph of the West.
