<h2>D<font size=-1>OSSIER:<br></font> T<font size=-1>HE</font> S<font size=-1>ECRET</font> H<font size=-1>ISTORY</font> <font size=-1>OF</font> A<font size=-1>RMAND</font> H<font size=-1>AMMER</font>.<br></h2>
<p> By Edward Jay Epstein. <br>
<i>Random House; 418 pages; $30</i><p>
<a href="12jb372.html">Jacket Copy</a>
<p><b>Biography</p></b>
EDWARD JAY EPSTEIN studied government at Cornell a Harvard, and taught political science at Harvard, MIT, a UCLA. He is the author of twelve books, includi Inquest: The Warren Commission and the Establishment of Tr and Deception: The Invisible War Between the KGB and the ClA.
